text: Rachel Dratch (born February 22 1966 in Lexington, Massachusetts) is an American comedy actress. She works mostly in television programs. She was on Saturday Night Live from 1999 to 2006. She was also in the sitcoms 30 Rock and Frasier. Category:Actors from Massachusetts Category:Comedians from Massachusetts Category:1966 births Category:Living people
